  id M-88e4d24fc4ae
  lemma logarithm
  language en
  sources (wiktionary)
  sense
    part_of_speech noun
    gloss "For a number x, the power to which a given base number must be raised in order to obtain x. Written \\log_b x. For example, \\log_{10} 1000 = 3 because 10^3 = 1000 and \\log_2 16 = 4 because 2^4 = 16."
    provenance (wiktionary)
